title: [Bloodriven Village, Blot Alley]
description: The narrow walkway is filled with shadows as the buildings on either side rise like overbearing lookouts.  A barrel sits rotting against the brick wall, bits of flaking plaster sticking to the disintegrating wood.

The snowy walkway is filled with shadows as the buildings on either side rise like overbearing lookouts.  A barrel sits rotting against the brick wall, the faint scent of cinnamon and stale whiskey permeating the disintegrating wood.
